features.value: A Catalan noble and politician, Oleguer Pujol i Drago was born in Barcelona in 1950. He studied law and economics and became a prominent figure in Catalan politics and business. He was involved in several controversies, including tax evasion and money laundering, which led to his resignation from political office.
